# RQ-53-20-03-006: Damage Tolerance 150mm

## Requirement Statement
The BWB outer skin panels shall maintain residual strength with damage up to 150mm length detectable by inspection.

## Rationale
CS-25.571 damage tolerance requirement for fail-safe structure.

## Acceptance Criteria
- Residual strength ≥ limit load with 150mm crack
- Two-bay crack criterion maintained
- Crack growth to critical size > 2× inspection interval

## Compliance Status
Analysis in progress, test planned Q4 2026

## Traceability
Parent: CS-25.571
